blogPost.excerpt: Design Cell is a growing collection of elements and styles for iOS app creation. The first version includes more than 800 elements and 20 ready-to-use sample screens. Experience a convenient workflow in your favorite design area and get things done faster.
blogPost.body: Design Cell is a growing collection of elements and styles for iOS app creation. The first version includes more than 800 elements and 20 ready-to-use sample screens. Experience a convenient workflow in your favorite design area and get things done faster.

blogPost.author: Anastasiya Yavorskaya

localize.description: Design Cell是一个不断增长的iOS应用创建元素和样式的集合。第一个版本包括800多个元素和20个随时可用的样屏。在您喜爱的设计区域体验便捷的工作流程，更快地完成任务。

previous.excerpt: Prop Hero is an interactive gaming platform that allows fans of live sports to compete in the action by correctly predicting what is going to happen while they watch. Prop Hero can be embedded into broadcast streams or used as a second screen experience.
previous.title: Prop Hero - Interactive predictor games for live sports

localize.description: Prop Hero是一个互动游戏平台，让体育直播的粉丝们在观看的同时，通过正确预测将要发生的事情来进行竞争。Prop Hero可以嵌入到直播流中，也可以作为第二屏体验使用。
localize.tagline: 体育直播的互动预测游戏

localize.description: Prop Hero是一個互動遊戲平臺，讓體育直播的粉絲們在觀看的同時，通過正確預測將要發生的事情來進行競爭。Prop Hero可以嵌入到直播流中，也可以作爲第二屏體驗使用。
localize.tagline: 體育直播的互動預測遊戲
